-------------------------------------------------------------

Replication Controller ->
Keep montoring the pod and if it fails/down then initiate new

Diff between scale up/down & scale out/in

RC vs RS (Replica Set)
----------------------
RC - Equality Based selection i.e. == !=
RS - Set/rule based selector

